## cozy navigation

* ctrl-s to visit a spartan space
* ctrl-g to visit a gemini capsule
* ctrl-n to visit a nex station
* ctrl-e to edit the current url
* ctrl-l to follow a link using a shortcut
* ctrl-r to refresh the current page
* ctrl-y to bookmark the current page
* ctrl-o to show bookmarks
* ctrl-h to get back to this page ðŸ™ƒ
* shift-left to go back to the previous page (no forward!)
* . to cancel a request

## cozy arguments

```ksh
$ cozy                  # get cozy
$ cozy blekksprut.net   # head straight to blekksprut.net
$ cozy -b               # edit bookmarks in your editor
$ cozy -t night         # nighttime *all the time*
```

