## cozy bookmarks

bookmarks are stored as a regular gemtext file
new bookmarks are added as new link lines at the end of the file

```
# cozy bookmarks

=> gemini://bbs.geminispace.org/
```

the bookmarks file can be customized to your liking outside of cozy

